==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Expugn
<hw>Ex*pugn"</hw> <pr>(⟦ecr⟧ks*p⟦umac⟧n")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<ety>[L. <ets>expugnare</ets>; <ets>ex</ets> out + <ets>pugnare</ets> to
fight, <ets>pugna</ets> fight. Cf. <er>Impugn</er>.]</ety> <def>To take
by assault; to storm; to overcome; to vanquish; <as>as, to
<ex>expugn</ex> cities; to <ex>expugn</ex> a person by
arguments.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Expugnable</ent>⟦br⟧
